Thank you.
<SYNC Start=935657><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=942808><P Class=ENCC>
What?
<SYNC Start=944969><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=946345><P Class=ENCC>
-You don't want to see this, do you?<br>-Hell, yeah!
<SYNC Start=950042><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=951050><P Class=ENCC>
I am not gonna show you this.
<SYNC Start=953575><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
