Come on now, think!
<SYNC Start=969333><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=970102><P Class=ENCC>
It's Rachel's tape,<br>and she can do whatever she wants.
<SYNC Start=974368><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=974573><P Class=ENCC>
And she wants to destroy it,<br>so end of story.
<SYNC Start=979067><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=979345><P Class=ENCC>
-I want to see it.<br>-What?
<SYNC Start=983111><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=983349><P Class=ENCC>
You don't want us to see this.
<SYNC Start=985510><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=985851><P Class=ENCC>
You so badly don't want us to see it<br>that it makes me want to see it.
<SYNC Start=992086><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=994226><P Class=ENCC>
Are we watching the tape or not?
<SYNC Start=997195><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=997896><P Class=ENCC>
-It's for your sake.<br>-I don't believe you.
<SYNC Start=1003562><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1003769><P Class=ENCC>
I think you don't want them<br>to see you begging me.
<SYNC Start=1007398><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1008707><P Class=ENCC>
-Rachel, please?<br>-Oh, a little preview.
<SYNC Start=1012609><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1014246><P Class=ENCC>
Fine. I want the record to show<br>that I tried to take the high road.
<SYNC Start=1019513><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1019752><P Class=ENCC>
Because in about five minutes,<br>I'm gonna be saying..
