Okay, here we go.
<SYNC Start=1032796><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1036135><P Class=ENCC>
I'm so happy.
<SYNC Start=1038535><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1041073><P Class=ENCC>
Thank God you're here. Help me.<br>Were you talking to yourself?
<SYNC Start=1044873><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1045044><P Class=ENCC>
-There I am.<br>-You're gonna get pregnant.
<SYNC Start=1049071><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1049748><P Class=ENCC>
I screwed up so bad.
<SYNC Start=1051443><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1051683><P Class=ENCC>
I told Monica that I'd send<br>those wedding invitations weeks ago.
<SYNC Start=1056950><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1057122><P Class=ENCC>
You didn't do it?
<SYNC Start=1058612><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1058857><P Class=ENCC>
I put them in my desk at work,<br>and forgot about them until today.
<SYNC Start=1064124><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1067199><P Class=ENCC>
Sweetie, it's okay. Everybody made it<br>to the wedding. I'm fine.
<SYNC Start=1072262><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1072538><P Class=ENCC>
-Kind of hurting my hand though.<br>-I know.
<SYNC Start=1076975><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1077209><P Class=ENCC>
I can 't believe it, especially after<br>Monica went on and on about it.
<SYNC Start=1082613><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
