It seems like yesterday<br>they just got engaged.
<SYNC Start=1127449><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1127693><P Class=ENCC>
I know.
<SYNC Start=1129524><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
