In about 5 seconds, you'll see why.
<SYNC Start=1180604><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1184383><P Class=ENCC>
Did I ever tell you about the time<br>I backpacked through Western Europe?
<SYNC Start=1190379><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1197262><P Class=ENCC>
Get ready to see some begging.
<SYNC Start=1200163><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1200866><P Class=ENCC>
