<SYNC Start=1204903><P Class=ENCC>
Now I'm so happy.
<SYNC Start=1207497><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1208407><P Class=ENCC>
-What?<br>-You used the Europe story!
<SYNC Start=1211843><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1212044><P Class=ENCC>
That's the magic story you use<br>when you want to have sex!
<SYNC Start=1216708><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
