<SYNC Start=1253879><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1254253><P Class=ENCC>
About that, the "who came on to who"<br>thing really doesn't matter.
<SYNC Start=1259919><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1260158><P Class=ENCC>
