<SYNC Start=1263127><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1263328><P Class=ENCC>
If you hadn't initiated it,<br>I know I would have.
<SYNC Start=1268425><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1269234><P Class=ENCC>
-It was an amazing night.<br>-It was. It was amazing.
<SYNC Start=1273432><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1275974><P Class=ENCC>
You think it looked amazing?
<SYNC Start=1279102><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
