<SYNC Start=1317142><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1317716><P Class=ENCC>
-There go the clothes.<br>-You are undressing awfully quickly.
<SYNC Start=1322380><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1322621><P Class=ENCC>
