<SYNC Start=1345172><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1347913><P Class=ENCC>
-Have you been working out?<br>-I have been working out.
<SYNC Start=1352714><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1354353><P Class=ENCC>
This is so much better<br>than I ever..
