Oh, that's not pretty.
<SYNC Start=1366520><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1367999><P Class=ENCC>
-Make it stop. Make it stop.<br>-Oh, no!
<SYNC Start=1371435><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1377209><P Class=ENCC>
Greg and Jenny's number<br>is totally different in here.
<SYNC Start=1380872><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1382781><P Class=ENCC>
-I don't ask too many questions, do I?<br>-No.
<SYNC Start=1385579><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1385751><P Class=ENCC>
-Really?<br>-Absolutely not.
<SYNC Start=1387082><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1387252><P Class=ENCC>
-Really?<br>-Oh, God.
<SYNC Start=1389379><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1391723><P Class=ENCC>
I bet that phone thing was some sort<br>of mix-up. I'm gonna call them.
<SYNC Start=1396023><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1399631><P Class=ENCC>
